reviewText:
Very good graphics, fun to play if you like the sport;
Happy that some bugs are fixed (all cars crashing in certain corners like monaco just after the tunnel)

Only one thing is hateful in this game : AI TIRE WEAR. It's totally unrealistic, on 100% race in Bahrein, Hamilton in the Mercedes did 22 laps on the option tire in the first stint with a heavier car and track thats not even rubbered in ! If you look at what Lewis actually did in Bahrein in 2013
